### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acme.local",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Set token (copy from login response)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get all positions
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get positions stats
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get position by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Create new position
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "TEST_POS",
  "name": "Test Position",
  "description": "For testing",
  "level": 99
}

### 5. Update position
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions/13
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Position Updated",
  "level": 100
}

### 6. Delete position
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions/13
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Try to delete position in use (should fail)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/v1/positions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
